    {
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "chapterTitle": "译本序",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "932154_3_7808-7828",
          "range": "7808-7828",
          "rangeStart": 7808,
          "rangeEnd": 7828,
          "markText": "上帝之所以被人原谅，因为上帝是不存在的。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1692836327,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-08-24 08:18:47",
          "chapterUid": 3,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=932154&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=7808&rangeEnd=7828",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/977324005e393a9776e1260?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=7808&rangeEnd=7828"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "932154_3_3616-3679",
          "range": "3616-3679",
          "rangeStart": 3616,
          "rangeEnd": 3679,
          "markText": "社会好像一根竹竿，分成若干节。一个人的伟大事业，就是爬上比他自己的阶级更高的阶级去，而上面那个阶级则利用一切力量阻止他爬上去。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1692836293,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-08-24 08:18:13",
          "chapterUid": 3,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=932154&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3616&rangeEnd=3679",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/977324005e393a9776e1260?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3616&rangeEnd=3679"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 37,
      "chapterTitle": "第二章 初入上流社会",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "932154_37_428-589",
          "range": "428-589",
          "rangeStart": 428,
          "rangeEnd": 589,
          "markText": "可笑而又感人的回忆：在十八岁上，孤零零，无依无靠地出现在头一个客厅啊！一个女人的眼光就足以使我惊慌失措。我越是想讨人喜欢，越是变得笨拙。我对一切形成了最错误的看法；要么我无缘无故地轻易信赖别人，要末我把一个人看成是敌人，因为他用严肃的眼光看了我。可是那时候，在我的羞怯造成的那些可怕的不幸中间，一个美好的日子是多么美好啊！",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1692789168,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-08-23 19:12:48",
          "chapterUid": 37,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=932154&chapterUid=37&rangeStart=428&rangeEnd=589",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/977324005e393a9776e1260?chapterUid=37&rangeStart=428&rangeEnd=589"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
